::CyberShark::

    He hugged Battera back and transformed to flight mode. In the air he sped 
up looking for any signs of Predacons. He remembered something from when he 
was Bazooka, Megatron was going to build a secret base somewhere, but he 
didn't know where.
    "Scan area for unit Megatron," CyberShark said to his computer. 
    "Unit Megatron not found," His computer said to him.
    "Then scan for Megatron on a repeating cycle of 5 nanoclicks," CyberShark 
said as he kicked his thrusters into maximum burn. "Also scan for Hell Beast."
